<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>New Provider Registration Requires Review</h1>
  
  <p>A new provider has submitted a registration that requires your review.</p>
  
  <h2>Registration Details:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Provider Name:</strong> <%= @registration.provider_name %></li>
    <li><strong>Category:</strong> <%= @registration.category_display_name %></li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @registration.email %></li>
    <li><strong>Submitted:</strong> <%= @registration.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>Submitted Information:</h2>
  <div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px;">
    <% @registration.submitted_data.each do |key, value| %>
      <p><strong><%= key.titleize %>:</strong> <%= value %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  
  <h2>Action Required:</h2>
  <p>Please review this registration and either approve or reject it. You can do this through your admin dashboard or by using the API endpoints:</p>
  
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Approve:</strong> POST /api/v1/provider_registrations/<%= @registration.id %>/approve</li>
    <li><strong>Reject:</strong> POST /api/v1/provider_registrations/<%= @registration.id %>/reject</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>If rejecting, please provide a clear reason for the rejection.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  Autism Services Locator System</p>
</body>
</html> 